<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是不這樣仔～細注意看，<delay20 />
流星可是會<delay8 />馬上溜走喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望我的願望可以成真……<delay20 />
希望我的願望可以成真<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay20 />這下不管流星什麼時候來<delay8 />都OK！</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為不知道流星什麼時候會來，<delay8 />
讓我連眨眼的空檔都沒有呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
眼睛都變乾啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣看著彩虹，<delay8 />就覺得心靈被洗滌了呢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是因為雨剛停，<delay8 />
才讓人特別這麼覺得嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看！<delay20 />好漂亮的彩虹啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然它終究會<delay8 />消失得無影無蹤，<delay20 />
但現在我們就好好欣賞吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真希望能騎著機車奔馳，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到那道彩虹的對面去啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到竟然能一次看到兩道彩虹，<delay20 />
真是個好兆頭呢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望能有更幸運的事<delay8 />等在後頭啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你看你看！<delay8 />那彩虹<delay20 />竟然有兩道耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底是怎麼變成那樣的啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">彩虹都會<delay8 />不知不覺就消失無蹤，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以得趁現在<delay8 />看～個清楚才行呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="004_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在想，<delay20 />極光的顏色……<delay20 />
還真是華麗啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />實在亂有幹勁的呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">要在天空掛上一層簾幕<delay20 />可是很辛苦的啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大自然……<delay20 />真是不可小看呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真是幸好<delay20 />我有來看極光啊！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />漂亮到<delay8 />讓我都忘了天氣有多冷哩！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="005_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也看一下吧！<delay20 />是飛機雲！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道是往哪裡飛啊？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />飛機雲好棒喔！<delay frames="40" />
既純白又勇往直前<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真希望我的心<delay8 />也能像它那樣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對不起喔，<delay frames="40" />
我現在<delay20 />正拼命在看飛機雲哩！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在它消失之前，你也來看看吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="006_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">今天總覺得內心<delay8 />有股騷動不安呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越是這種時候，就越要看看月亮，<delay8 />
讓自己冷靜下來才行，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">月亮圓形的光<delay8 />好像頭燈喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到它竟然用這麼明亮的光照亮我們，<delay20 />
看來月亮也拿出了幹勁啊～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看著那圓圓的月亮，<delay frames="40" />
我就會覺得<delay20 /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<tag a="110" b="0" />好想吃鬆餅喔～<delay frames="30" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之類的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>